replyContent: Hi Benny, this has very likely to do with the fact that your photos are on an external SD card on your device and PhotoSync needs permissions to 'write' (includes deleting) to your SD card. Please get the permissions in the PhotoSync settings under "Expert settings", "Write permissions for PhotoSync on external SD card" and it will work.
